<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to {{ app_name }}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f0f0f0;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2563eb;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 30px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #059669;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            border-top: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
            padding-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .feature-list {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .feature-item {
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .feature-item:before {
            content: "âœ“";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #059669;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">{{ app_name }}</div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h1>Welcome to {{ app_name }}! ðŸŽ‰</h1>
        
        <p>Hello {{ user.firstName }},</p>
        
        <p>We're excited to welcome you to {{ app_name }}, the modern design platform that empowers you to create stunning visuals effortlessly!</p>
        
        <div class="feature-list">
            <h3>What you can do with {{ app_name }}:</h3>
            <div class="feature-item">Create professional designs with our intuitive editor</div>
            <div class="feature-item">Access thousands of templates and design elements</div>
            <div class="feature-item">Export your designs in multiple formats</div>
            <div class="feature-item">Collaborate with team members in real-time</div>
            <div class="feature-item">Store and organize your media files</div>
            <div class="feature-item">Integrate with AI-powered tools</div>
        </div>
        
        <p>Ready to start creating? Click the button below to access your dashboard:</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{ dashboard_url }}" class="button">Start Creating</a>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you have any questions or need help getting started, our support team is here to help. You can also check out our:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Getting Started Guide</li>
            <li>Video Tutorials</li>
            <li>Community Forum</li>
            <li>Knowledge Base</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p>Thank you for choosing {{ app_name }}. We can't wait to see what you create!</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The {{ app_name }} Team</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This email was sent to {{ user.email }}. You're receiving this because you recently created an account with us.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
